<p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  Congratulations! You have experienced FixMyStreet from both the citizen and council perspectives.
  In 20 minutes, you have seen how residents report problems, how councils manage them, and the
  AWS architecture that powers it all.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you've learned</h2>

<div class="ndx-takeaway-grid">
  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">📍</span>
      Citizen engagement
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      FixMyStreet makes it easy for residents to report problems in under 2 minutes.
      Map-based reporting with categories and photos gives councils precise, actionable
      information without lengthy phone calls.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Residents get a simple, accessible way to report issues 24/7
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">📊</span>
      Council efficiency
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      The council dashboard and admin panel turn citizen reports into structured work items.
      Spatial views help identify patterns, category filters enable triage, and status
      tracking provides accountability.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Councils can manage street issues efficiently with real-time visibility
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">🔓</span>
      Open source value
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      FixMyStreet is built on proven open-source technology maintained by mySociety
      and used by thousands of councils worldwide. No vendor lock-in, transparent code,
      and a large community contributing improvements.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Proven technology with no licensing costs and full customisation freedom
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">☁️</span>
      Cloud-native architecture
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Running on AWS Fargate, Aurora PostgreSQL, EFS, and CloudFront means no servers
      to maintain. Managed services handle patching, backups, scaling, and availability
      automatically.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Production-ready infrastructure with no operational overhead
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

